description:
This is a 13 minute workout called 'SUPERMODEL 10 MINUTE INTERVAL RUN | Treadmill Follow Along with IBX Running' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Today we are crushing this quick 10 minute treadmill interval run by Danish supermodel Nina Agdal! She is super passionate about the fitness space and we love this walk-run hill interval workout! Coach Rachael will take you through it

12:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com

11:40 - Cool Down
